contentrichtext.text: {{Speciesbox |taxon = Xanthorrhoea quadrangulata |image = Xanthorrhoea quadrangulata HRM1.jpg |authority = }} '''''Xanthorrhoea quadrangulata''''' is a plant in the genus [[Xanthorrhoea]]. ==Gallery== {{Gallery | title = | lines = 4 |File:Yaccas at Parra Wirra 1.JPG|alt1=Yaccas1|''X. quadrangulata'' growing in crevices in granite gneiss outcrop at [[Para Wirra Recreation Park|Parra Wirra]], South Australia |File:Yaccas at Parra Wirra 2.JPG|alt1=Yaccas2|''X. quadrangulata'' growing in crevice in granite gneiss outcrop at [[Para Wirra Recreation Park|Parra Wirra]], South Australia }} {{Commonscat|Xanthorrhoea quadrangulata}} [[Category:Xanthorrhoeoideae]] {{Asparagales-stub}}
